'''2009年孟加拉國總統選舉'''在{{link-en|2008年孟加拉國大選|2008 Bangladeshi general election|2008年大選}}後，預訂於2009年2月16日舉行。<ref>{{cite web | first=Liyu | last=Lin | url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-01/29/content_10734225.htm | title=Bangladesh's new president to be elected on Feb. 16 | language=en | date=2009-01-29 | access-date= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110820093919/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2009-01/29/content_10734225.htm | archive-date=2011-08-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6570641.html | title=Bangladesh's new parliament to hold 1st session on Jan. 25 | language=en | date=2009-01-08 | access-date= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201052805/http://en.people.cn/90001/90777/90851/6570641.html | archive-date=2020-02-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>選舉原訂於2007年9月5日[[亚杰丁·艾哈迈德|亚杰丁·艾哈迈德]]任期屆滿前舉行，但由於沒有選國會，總統選舉亦因此推遲。<ref>{{cite web | first=Mark | last=Dummett | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/6979350.stm | title=Bangladesh president to continue | publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] | date=2007-09-05 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904063846/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/6979350.stm | archive-date=2020-09-04 | dead-url=no | accessdate=2020-09-30 }}</ref>在國會選舉中獲勝的[[孟加拉國人民聯盟|孟加拉國人民聯盟]]提名[[齐勒·拉赫曼|齐勒·拉赫曼]]為總統候選人，並預計會接受國會選舉<ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6566372.html | title=Awami League's senior leader Zillur Rahman to become Bangladesh's next president | language=en | date=2009-01-04 | access-date= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201052810/http://en.people.cn/90001/90777/90851/6566372.html | archive-date=2020-02-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。由於截至2009年2月9日提名候選人的截止日期，仍只有他被提名<ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6588123.html | title=Zillur Rahman becomes only candidate for Bangladeshi presidential election | language=en | date=2009-02-09 | access-date= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201052805/http://en.people.cn/90001/90777/90851/6588123.html | archive-date=2020-02-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而他亦沒有在2月11日限期前取消登記參選。孟加拉国选举委员会隨即宣佈他當選新任總統。他在12日宣誓就職。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://en.people.com.cn/90001/90777/90851/6590659.html | title=Zillur Rahman declared as Bangladesh's new President | language=en | date=2009-02-11 | access-date= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201052759/http://en.people.cn/90001/90777/90851/6590659.html | archive-date=2020-02-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2009-02-11/183617194855.shtml | title=齐勒-拉赫曼成为孟加拉国新总统 | language=zh-cn | date=2009-02-11 | access-date=2020-09-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930120040/https://news.sina.com.cn/w/2009-02-11/183617194855.shtml | archive-date=2020-09-30 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

